12 (9) the potential for adverse impacts on air quality to include, frequent and unwarranted
13 smoke, and strong and obnoxious odors.
14 (b) Not later than 6 months after the effective date of this act, the department shall
15 promulgate or revise any such rules and regulations necessary to implement the provisions of this
16 section.
